track_notes:
The route up to Kiowa Mountain from the interesting  Canon Plaza area. If the gate below the lookout is locked you will have a hike of ~ half a mile. If the gate is open its a drive up. 

Kiowa can also be reached from the north side by driving SW from US 64.
The route from Kiowa to Hwy 64.

Turns out FR 45 is in better shape and shorter than either the roads from Canon Plaza or Hwy 64. The route has various markings on different maps. If I recall correctly the turnoff from the paved 111 is marked FR 45.
